# JotForm Integration

Schema is fetched by parsing form HTML (no API key). Proxy forwards form body to JotForm submit URL.

**Properties reference**: https://api.jotform.com/docs/properties/index.php

Field names from HTML: fullname uses q{n}_first, q{n}_last; address uses q{n}_addr_line1, city, etc.
